</header>

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
            LeanCorp Foundation is a Malawi-based non-profit organization focused on
            strengthening agricultural cooperatives through operational excellence and
            process improvement.
        </p>

        <h3>Mission</h3>
        <p>
            To improve the efficiency, sustainability, and governance of agricultural
            cooperatives using Lean Six Sigma methodologies.
        </p>

        <h3>Vision</h3>
        <p>
            Efficient, resilient, and farmer-centered cooperatives driving sustainable
            rural livelihoods.
        </p>

        <h3>Leadership</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt</li>
            <li>Project Management Professional (PMP®)</li>
            <li>MBA – Rochester Institute of Technology (USA)</li>
            <li>Currently enrolled in a Diploma in Mechanical Engineering</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

