<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Lean Six Sigma DMAIC</h2>
        <p>
            All LeanCorp Foundation projects use the
            <strong>DMAIC methodology</strong> to drive sustainable improvement.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card"><h3>Define</h3><p>Clarify problems affecting efficiency and farmer income.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Measure</h3><p>Collect baseline performance data.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Analyze</h3><p>Identify root causes of inefficiencies.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Improve</h3><p>Redesign workflows and optimize equipment.</p></div>
            <div class="card"><h3>Control</h3><p>Sustain gains through SOPs and monitoring.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

